<DOCNO> LA012594-0169 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 007033 </DOCID>
<SOURCE>
<P>
 Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</SOURCE>
<DATE>
<P>
January 25, 1994, Tuesday, Ventura West Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Metro; Part B; Page 1; Column 2 
</P>
</SECTION>
