<P>
 * Blood donations: 
</P>
<P>
 Donating blood takes about an hour. People wishing to donate should be at 
least 18 years old, weigh more than 110 pounds and be in good health. For blood 
donation sites: 
</P>
<P>
 * American Red Cross (800) 974-2113 
</P>
