<HEADLINE>
<P>
COUNTYWIDE FOCUS: AIDE TO HART HOLDING WEEKLY OFFICE HOURS 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
By KAY SAILLANT 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 An aide to state Sen. Gary K. Hart is holding weekly office hours at the 
County Government Center in Ventura to answer queries from the public, the 
legislator said. 
</P>
<P>
 Beverly O'Gorman will meet with citizens from 10 a.m. to noon Thursdays on the 
fourth floor of the administration building at 800 S. Victoria Ave., said Hart 
(D-Santa Barbara). 
</P>
<P>
 The office hours will continue each Thursday until Hart's term ends next 
January. 
</P>
<P>
 No appointment is necessary. 
</P>
<P>
 Anyone with a question or comment about state agencies or upcoming legislation 
is encouraged to drop by, Hart said. Hart's district includes the Ventura 
County cities of Ojai, Santa Paula and Ventura. KAY SAILLANT 
