<DOCNO> LA012594-0186 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 007050 </DOCID>
<SOURCE>
<P>
 Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</SOURCE>
<DATE>
<P>
January 25, 1994, Tuesday, Ventura West Edition 
</P>
