REGIONAL ROUNDUP: ONETIME CHARGE RESULTS IN FORTUNE PETROLEUM LOSS 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Fortune Petroleum Corp. in Agoura Hills said it will take a onetime special 
charge of $1.9 million in the fourth quarter to reflect lower oil prices, 
resulting in a significant loss for its just-completed fiscal year. 
