19 Rape 73 75 55 Robbery 518 569 464 Assault 1,051 965 908 Burglary 2,120 2,134 
1,615 Theft 5,025 5,145 4,425 Auto Theft 981 1,109 1,148 Arson 51 50 56 Totals 
